  {desc:"实现简单的模板字符串替换", template:'# 模板替换\n', hint:'def template(text, **kwargs):\n    for key, val in kwargs.items():\n        text = text.replace("{" + key + "}", str(val))\n    return text\nresult = template("你好{name}，你{age}岁了", name="小明", age=10)\nprint(result)', check:function(o){return o.indexOf("小明")!==-1;}},
  {desc:"反转句子中的每个单词但保持顺序", template:'# 单词反转\n', hint:'def reverse_words(sentence):\n    return " ".join(w[::-1] for w in sentence.split())\nprint(reverse_words("Hello World Python"))', check:function(o){return o.indexOf("olleH")!==-1;}},
  {desc:"检查两个字符串是否是变位词", template:'# 变位词\n', hint:'def is_anagram(a, b):\n    return sorted(a.lower()) == sorted(b.lower())\nprint(is_anagram("listen", "silent"))\nprint(is_anagram("hello", "world"))', check:function(o){return o.indexOf("True")!==-1 && o.indexOf("False")!==-1;}},
  {desc:"实现字符串压缩（如aabcccccaaa → a2b1c5a3）", template:'# 字符串压缩\n', hint:'def compress(s):\n    if not s: return ""\n    result = []\n    count = 1\n    for i in range(1, len(s)):\n        if s[i] == s[i-1]: count += 1\n        else:\n            result.append(s[i-1] + str(count))\n            count = 1\n    result.append(s[-1] + str(count))\n    return "".join(result)\nprint(compress("aabcccccaaa"))', check:function(o){return o.indexOf("a2b1c5a3")!==-1;}},
  {desc:"综合：实现一个简单的Markdown→纯文本转换器", template:'# MD转文本\n', hint:'def md_to_text(md):\n    result = []\n    for line in md.split("\\n"):\n        line = line.lstrip("#").strip()\n        line = line.replace("**","").replace("*","").replace("`","")\n        if line: result.append(line)\n    return "\\n".join(result)\nmd = "# 标题\\n\\n**加粗**文本和*斜体*\\n\\n`代码`片段"\nprint(md_to_text(md))', check:function(o){return o.indexOf("标题")!==-1;}}
